{"tid":1892991,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【蘋果踢爆】三區批62萬飲飲食食 參與資格神秘只益自己人","createTime":"2020-02-23T02:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T03:11:18.000Z","uid":5191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cda5a4c4bf4cec911d2c6e90e27135413a645483","tid":1892991,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"區議會每年掌控數以億元公帑，部份活動只有「小圈子」受惠。《蘋果》清查全港18個區議會，發現最少三區，包括沙田、黃大仙和西貢區均曾使用公帑舉辦僅限獲邀人士出席的活動，合共使用逾62萬元。有議會新丁表明希望今屆不再舉辦此類活動，「盡量都唔好再勞民傷財，搞呢啲同民生無關痛癢嘅活動。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200223/PQGY4VK2B3V33TCE7T5JNOPS2Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200223%2FPQGY4VK2B3V33TCE7T5JNOPS2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdguzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=23685e54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200223%2FPQGY4VK2B3V33TCE7T5JNOPS2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a3ec8e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200223/PQGY4VK2B3V33TCE7T5JNOPS2Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"2923952a851e66ba0f36b8e1277bfddbcfa5e813","tid":1892991,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"百萬led燈牌？"},{"pid":"bfc17d9abc5937ce29d46b30c1ab2f88546ec224","tid":1892991,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2923952a851e66ba0f36b8e1277bfddbcfa5e813","tid":1892991,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"百萬led燈牌？"},"citedBy":0,"repl